{"tid":1371583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方將於短時間內展開驅散行動（2019-07-27）","createTime":"2019-07-27T09:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T09:49:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"78c811ca137b99a7193ab2707298cc52033015fb","tid":1371583,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"警方將於短時間內展開驅散行動<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n<br />\n  現時（七月二十七日）元朗南邊圍一帶有人聚集及起哄，他們手持鐵枝、自製盾牌，甚至拆毀路邊的鐵欄。另外，現場有人包圍及破壞警車，車上警務人員的生命安全受到威脅。<br />\n<br />\n  鑑於現場情況持續惡化，警方將於短時間內展開驅散行動，防線會由西向東面推進，請市民向西鐵元朗站方向離去。市民如非必要請不要前往元朗區，並小心注意自身安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月27日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間17時13分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/27/P2019072700682.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F27%2FP2019072700682.htm&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT18bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=797078cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/27/P2019072700682.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8938a74b766013e71ff2eb30d5392d06da13e4df","tid":1371583,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcde973ac6d74eb7494190f738fbe4deab2a4d5d","tid":1371583,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7af953662c583b3124b5ca3ae01312e8e060858","tid":1371583,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:42:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>【今晚 7:07 日落】手足！日落前好散！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1371250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1371250</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0fae0e7f9449