開驅散行動，防線會由西向東面推進，請市民向西鐵元朗站方向離去。市民如非必要請不要前往元朗區，並小心注意自身安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月27日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間17時13分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/27/P2019072700682.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F27%2FP2019072700682.htm&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT18bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=797078cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/27/P2019072700682.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"一路出警告一路射彈，好撚野"},{"pid":"1cea3db2b28b08f30fe66c7fa1c061a2bb5b0ecf","tid":1371583,"uid":153980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:45:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5febf651aca0adf732ab141b676fdf492c844e3","tid":1371583,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fa6c7db9d2af85b747c70b2c4f574f45903dfd","tid":1371583,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1d5215e22bd712490e39667e98e7ff153648c9","tid":1371583,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdc07923040ee8e887e26c621340571d1898ec6","tid":1371583,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"巴打們 小心丫"},{"pid":"793d1ecd4139eb959ba7ea1a666b6ea2e537df6d","tid":1371583,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a14fe0257cd9befdf10299a63a18d909cbf86a3","tid":1371583,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:49:07.000Z